<div id="review_1161111971" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/1161111971" />
    <a title="Lorraine Carey" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/5661003-lorraine-carey"><img alt="Lorraine Carey" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1516905235p2/5661003.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/1161111971?book_show_action=true">Jan 08, 2015</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Lorraine Carey" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Lorraine Carey" href="/user/show/5661003-lorraine-carey">Lorraine Carey</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Kindle Edition " href="/book/show/23876270-ancient-truth">review of another edition</a>


        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1161111971" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer13028131690887776978">ANCIENT TRUTH is a compelling and very interesting story about the beginning of this <br/>planet&apos;s history. The arrival of the first conquerors and the creation of the first <br/>kingdom are just a small part of a new, surely to be, best selling saga. Fearless Anu,the first Fallen Angel, the devil, the pure evil, starts a war against his brothers, <br/>the Angels, with the intention of becoming the new God of this and many others <br/>Galaxies. As the story reveals itself, you&apos;ll find many well aimed interpretation</span>
  <span id="freeText13028131690887776978" style="display:none">ANCIENT TRUTH is a compelling and very interesting story about the beginning of this <br />planet's history. The arrival of the first conquerors and the creation of the first <br />kingdom are just a small part of a new, surely to be, best selling saga. Fearless Anu,the first Fallen Angel, the devil, the pure evil, starts a war against his brothers, <br />the Angels, with the intention of becoming the new God of this and many others <br />Galaxies. As the story reveals itself, you'll find many well aimed interpretations of <br />myths, actual history, even urban legends, which make you imagine a completely <br />different and vivid scenario of how our past could have been. As pages keep turning <br />you'll be thrilled with Jack's imagination and capability to put together such a <br />complex and marvelous story. I can't wait for the sequel that, as I imagine, will bring <br />much more surprises and unexpected twists like this truly unique story already did.</span>
  <a data-text-id="13028131690887776978" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
